Island: Jianfeng Mountain),
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8B36F96F75FF9C0DA9FD41FEBEFD5F" blockId="3.[190,1399,597,800]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<taxonomicName id="4C344D7A6F75FF9C0DA9FD41FC3DFD7B" authority="Meng &amp; Wang, 2012" authorityName="Meng &amp; Wang" authorityYear="2012" box="[190,963,702,729]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Gergithus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nonomaculatus" subGenus="Maculergithus">
